      "writtenOn": "2026-04-15T21:48:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do we really to fetch again *all* files between patch-sets?\nYou have the `filesApprovedByOwners` and this function should just return the ones that were *automatically* approved.\n\nAlso, we do not need to get *all* files, but only the ones that are approved by an owner who is the \"change owner\".\n\n```suggestion\n    Set\u003cString\u003e filesTouchedByChangeOwner \u003d fileExpandedOwners.entrySet().stream()\n            .filter(entry -\u003e ownerIds(entry.getValue()).anyMatch(id -\u003e id \u003d\u003d ownerId))\n            .map(Map.Entry::getKey)\n            .collect(Collectors.toSet());\n```",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 276,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 279,
        "endChar": 96
      },
      "revId": "55e3c786ec2d465be2900dd150fc1f340a723805",
