        "id": 1072905
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-04-16T17:09:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We are only interested in the files changed between patchsets (for example PS2 vs PS3).\n\n`allowsAutoApprovalOnPatch` checks whether, in the last PS, only the change owner-owned files were modified.\n\nIf we were filtering on `fileExpandedOwners`, we would get _all_ files in the _change_ (filtered by the change owner).\n\nI thought I had covered this by tests, but apparently I didn\u0027t (or not properly).\nI will also check if there is way to obtain what we need by filtering what we already computed.",
      "parentUuid": "ccc01e0b_7e7c9e97",
